马克·罗森的角色不会出现在电影《重返黑色》中https://www.nme.com/news/film/mark-ronsons-character-will-not-be-in-the-back-to-black-film-3611658?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mark-ronsons-角色不会出现在黑色电影中Surej SinghMon, 01 Apr 2024 03:31:55 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3611658 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>导演萨姆·泰勒-约翰逊证实“马克·朗森这个角色从未在电影中出现过”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mark-ronsons-character-will-not-be-in-the-back-to-black-film-3611658">马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 的角色将不会出现在电影《Back To Black》中，这一消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>尽管马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse</a> ) 2006 年专辑《Back To Black》中扮演了关键角色，但已证实<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mark-ronson">马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson)</a>这个角色不会出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/back-to-black">即将上映的同名电影</a>中。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/amy-winehouse-songs-back-to-black-frank-lioness-3610687">艾米怀恩豪斯的故事——歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>加拿大演员杰夫·通克在接受<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-13255799/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse-black-biopic.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日邮报》</em></a>采访时表示，他饰演罗森的场景已全部从最终电影中删除，此消息得到确认。根据通克的说法，被删减的场景也导致他的作品从电影和 IMDb 中删除。</p><p>然而，该片导演山姆·泰勒-约翰逊<a href="https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-13255799/mark-ronson-amy-winehouse-black-biopic.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">随后通过发言人回应</a>称：“马克·朗森这个角色从未在电影中出现过，所以不可能‘删掉所有涉及马克·朗森的场景’”因为它们不存在。”</p><p> Ronson 是 Winehouse 的朋友和合作者，帮助制作了她影响深远的第二张专辑，即 2006 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/amy-winehouses-back-to-black-just-turned-10-years-old-but-it-matters-more-than-ever-1780826#:~:text=Anyway%2C%20I%20distinctly%20remember%20thinking,there's%20no%20filler%20at%20all.">《Back To Black》</a> 。虽然罗森与这部电影的制作没有关系，但他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-ronson-shares-thoughts-amy-winehouse-biopic-back-to-black-3571532">今年早些时候透露，他已经阅读了这部电影的剧本</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3571575" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3571575" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3571575" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MarkRonson-Amy-Winehouse-biopic-Back-To-Black-thoughts.jpg" alt="马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 和艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse) 一起在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MarkRonson-Amy-Winehouse-biopic-Back-To-Black-thoughts.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MarkRonson-Amy-Winehouse-biopic-Back-To-Black-thoughts-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MarkRonson-Amy-Winehouse-biopic-Back-To-Black-thoughts-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MarkRonson-Amy-Winehouse-biopic-Back-To-Black-thoughts-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MarkRonson-Amy-Winehouse-biopic-Back-To-Black-thoughts-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MarkRonson-Amy-Winehouse-biopic-Back-To-Black-thoughts-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3571575" class="wp-caption-text">马克·罗森和艾米·怀恩豪斯现场表演。图片来源：JMEnternational/Redferns/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> “我对这部电影唯一了解的是我非常了解山姆，我读了剧本，我觉得它做得非常好......我想起了[怀恩豪斯]的幽默，它真的很吸引人，”他谈到电影。 “我认为她有一种聪明的幽默感，这是她的众多天赋之一，他们在电影中表现得非常好。我很期待看到它。”</p><p>这部电影由萨姆·泰勒-约翰逊执导，玛丽莎·阿贝拉（ <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/industry">《工业》</a></em> ）饰演怀恩豪斯，讲述了这位标志性歌手在伦敦的充满活力的岁月，以及她的成名之路。该片将于 2024 年 4 月 12 日在英国和爱尔兰上映。</p><p>除了阿贝拉之外，这部传记片还由杰克·奥康奈尔饰演怀恩豪斯的前夫布莱克·菲尔德-西维尔，埃迪·马森饰演米奇，朱丽叶·考恩饰演她的母亲贾尼斯，莱斯利·曼维尔饰演她的祖母辛西娅。 </p><figure id="attachment_3380539" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3380539" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3380539" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black.jpg" alt="艾米·怀恩豪斯玛丽莎·阿贝尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/Marisa-Abel-Back-To-Black-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3380539" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽莎·阿贝拉 (Marisa Abela) 在《重返黑色》中饰演艾米·怀恩豪斯 (Amy Winehouse)。图片来源：Studiocanal</figcaption></figure><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soundtrack-announced-for-new-amy-winehouse-back-to-black-movie-including-original-song-by-nick-cave-3605389">我们分享了<em>《Back To Black》</em>官方原声带的详细信息</a>，其中包括歌手本人的歌曲以及其他标志性艺术家的歌曲。其中包括 2003 年首张专辑《Frank》中的三首歌曲、《Back To Black》中的另外三首歌曲，以及启发艾米灵感的艺术家的五首歌曲：The Shangri-Las、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-holiday">Billie Holiday</a> 、Minnie Riperton、Dinah Washington 和 Sarah沃恩。 </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_91 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_91" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/back-to-black-posters-amy-winehouse-3610218"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>这张合辑专辑名为《Back To Black: Songss from the Original Motion Picture》，将于 5 月 17 日通过 UMR/Island Records 发行。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/mark-ronsons-character-will-not-be-in-the-back-to-black-film-3611658">马克·罗森 (Mark Ronson) 的角色将不会出现在电影《Back To Black》中，这一消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
